### Reproducing Manuscript Figures ###

The run.sh scripts included in each subdirectory (Case1, Case2, Case2/fig8, and Case3) reproduce Figures 1–12 of the following manuscript:

Utsugi, M. (2026). Adaptive L1-Anisotropic Total Variation Regularization for 3D Magnetic Inversion. Computers & Geosciences (submitted).

# How to Run
Navigate to each subdirectory and execute the run.sh script.

Example:

cd Case1
./run.sh

For more detailed instructions, refer to the README file in each subdirectory.
